items.name: nashsu/FreeAskInternet
items.description: FreeAskInternet is a completely free, PRIVATE and LOCALLY running search aggregator & answer generate using MULTI LLMs, without GPU needed. The user can ask a question and the system will  make a multi engine search and combine the search result to LLM and generate the answer based on search results. It's all FREE to use.
